The '''Urban Development Institute of Australia''' ('''UDIA''') is an [[Education in Australia|education]] and [[non-profit organization|non-profit organisation]] with offices in [[Queensland]], [[New South Wales]], [[Victoria (Australia)|Victoria]], [[Western Australia]], [[South Australia]], [[Northern Territory]] and [[Australian Capital Territory]]. Its mission is to promote affordability, sustainability and certainty in the urban development and construction industry.

